<tr>
<td height="20" align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #89aa4d; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px;">For more information or to book the Fjord Explorer, please call 01483 79 11 11</td>
</tr>
